  {
    "Id": 10,
    "Content": "It will automatically prompt for password when necessary\n* This script will ask you to install firmware, bluetooth and wifi driver one by one\n* Tested on Ubuntu with linux 7.0 kernel\n\n### 🚀 Easy Automatic Fix (Recommended for Arch Based System)\nIf you want to quickly fix your WiFi and Bluetooth on any modern kernel, follow these steps:\n\nMake the script executable if not already",
    "ContentSha": "mePv+dKi33GgBsipTP7w17LuKK0uJFEcWDnOzcT3CuI=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "必要に応じて自動的にパスワードを求められます  \n* このスクリプトはファームウェア、Bluetooth、WiFiドライバーのインストールを順番に案内します  \n* Ubuntuのlinux 7.0カーネルでテスト済み  \n\n### 🚀 簡単自動修正（Archベースのシステムに推奨）  \n最新のカーネルでWiFiとBluetoothを素早く修正したい場合は、以下の手順に従ってください。  \n\nスクリプトをまだ実行可能にしていない場合は実行可能にする  ",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": false
  },
  {
    "Id": 11,
    "Content": "```\nchmod +x ./fix_my_wifi.sh\n```",
    "ContentSha": "TrDah6izESr6AgEsbTRKYlkukuyBf9MPB55vEobFX/w=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "```\nchmod +x ./fix_my_wifi.sh\n```",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": true
  },
  {
    "Id": 12,
    "Content": "\n**Run the automatic fix script** with sudo:",
    "ContentSha": "UiPa/5M43T3aK62fcUS3oNmPwQOobXxw0nlsj82W0/E=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "\n**sudoを付けて自動修正スクリプトを実行する**:",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": false
  },
  {
    "Id": 13,
    "Content": "```bash\nsudo bash fix_my_wifi.sh\n```",
    "ContentSha": "8jZMLY5xQrGecFaevLgLIqmw4VTIS7S9c3SVzsqH/N8=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "```bash\nsudo bash fix_my_wifi.sh\n```",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": true
